approximately half of which related to investments with stated maturities less
than 1 year as of september24, 2005 and net unrealized losses of $6.3
million on its investment portfolio, primarily related to investments with
stated maturities less than 1 year as of september25, 2004. the company
occasionally sells short-term investments prior to their stated maturities. the
company recognized a net loss before taxes of $137,000 in 2005 and net gains
